data.description: This stunning residence with a spacious layout designed for both relaxation and entertainment. Whether it's the view of the course from your front porch or your enjoying the centerpiece of your outdoor oasis with the private pool. Inside, discover a meticulously crafted interior featuring high-end finishes and modern amenities and fixtures. From the gourmet kitchen equipped with top-of-the-line appliances to the inviting living spaces bathed in natural light. Whether you're lounging poolside or enjoying a round of golf, Pointe West is more than just a residence—it's a lifestyle statement.
